      <hedline>
        <hl1>15 Filipinos Die in Revelry</hl1>
      </hedline>
      <byline class="print_byline">Reuters</byline>
      <dateline>MANILA, Jan. 1</dateline>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>LEAD: Thirteen people were killed and nearly 1,500 maimed, burned, shot or stabbed as Filipinos celebrated the New Year with fireworks and gunfire, the police and hospitals said. Doctors said they operated on 22 people hit by stray bullets.</p>
